    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>An Inconvenient Woman</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Michel Baranger letter praises David France's May 28 article on transsexual Calpernia Sarah Addams's courage in face of murder of Pfc Barry Winchell</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Many thanks to David France (May 28) for a deeply touching and unusual story. Congratulations to Calpernia Sarah Addams for her courage and for remaining faithful to her dream. May the horrible death of Pfc. Barry Winchell shock us all into realizing that the complexity of real life seldom reduces to absolute categories.</p>
        <p>Michel Baranger</p>
        <p>Cambridge, Mass</p>
      </block>
